title: The Canadians [1961 - UK] (Robert Ryan) western
description:
The Canadians (1961 - UK)

Western

starring . . . . Robert Ryan, John Dehner, Torin Thatcher
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0054715/


Filmed at Cypress Hills, Saskatchewan, Canada

General Custer had been annihilated by Sitting Bull and six thousand Sioux. Having killed Custer and his men, the Sioux fled north. North toward the medicine line and Canada. Filmed on the actual location, Cypress Hills Saskatchewan, the story is respectfully dedicated to the Northwest Mounted Police, without whose help the picture could not have been made. Without whose help Canada could not have survived.


Video: XviD, 720x544, 23.976 fps, 1981 Kbps, 01h23m56s
Audio: Dolby AC3, 48000 Hz, stereo, 256 kbps

VHSRip fullscreen, English audio, optional Croatian subtitles
